COMMENT - |FRAME: Pyrethrins Pyrethrins| are natural insecticides extracted from the seed cases of |FRAME: TAX-118510|, and are considered the most important natural pesticides economically.
/
/The chemical structure of pyrethrins inspired the production of a variety of synthetic insecticides called |FRAME: Pyrethroids pyrethroids|, such as |FRAME: CPD-22549|, |FRAME: CPD-22550|, and |FRAME: CPD-22551|. Pyrethrins are more environmentally friendly, less toxic, and less stable than the synthetic commercial pyrethroids, which are toxic to fish and other non-target organisms |CITS: [Haya89]|.
//
