/Alkanes are often classified by the length of their acyl moiety.
/
/|FRAME: Short-Chain-Alkanes  "Short-chain alkanes"| contain less than 6- carbons.
/
/|FRAME: Medium-Chain-Alkanes  "Medium-chain alkanes"| contain 6-12 carbons.
/
/|FRAME: Long-Chain-Alkanes "Long-chain alkanes"| contain 13-22 carbons.
/
/|FRAME: Very-Long-Chain-Alkanes  "Very-long-chain alkanes"| contain 23 carbons or longer.
