/|FRAME: GLUCOSAMINE-1P| isomers.  
/
/The enzyme is active only in phosphorylated form; the site of phosphorylation in the enzyme from |FRAME: TAX-562| is Ser102 |CITS: [10231382]|. it can autophosphorylate <I>in vitro</I> in the presence of ATP to a low level |CITS: [10671448]|. 
