/There are two major families of cutin monomers, comprising C16 and C18 compounds. The C16 family consists mainly of |FRAME: 16-HYDROXYPALMITATE| and |FRAME: CPD-17653| and |FRAME: 1016-DIHYDROXYPALMITATE|. The C18 family consists mainly of |FRAME: 18-HYDROXYOLEATE|, |FRAME: 910-EPOXY-18-HYDROXYSTEARATE|, and |FRAME: 91018-TRIHYDROXYSTEARATE|.
//
