/
/Examples include the GdnC protein of |FRAME: TAX-1238679|, which is involved in formation of |FRAME: Aminomalonyl-PCP|, the |FRAME: ENTF-MONOMER "EntF protein"| of |FRAME: TAX-562|, involved in |FRAME: ENTBACSYN-PWY|, and the ClbE protein that is involved in |FRAME: CPD-22719| biosynthesis..
