UNIQUE-ID - SULFOQUINOVOSYLDIACYLGLYCEROL
TYPES - Sulfolipids
TYPES - GLYCOSYLGLYCERIDES
COMMON-NAME - a 6-sulfo-&alpha;-D-quinovosyl diacylglycerol
