COMMENT - This is an advanced glycation end-product (AGE) generated by the spontaneous interaction of |FRAME: METHYL-GLYOXAL| with |FRAME: Protein-L-Arginines|. It is one of the major AGEs of human lens proteins |CITS: [14638728]|.
