COMMENT - All terpene indole alkaloids are derived from |FRAME: TRP| (via |FRAME: TRYPTAMINE|) and the iridoid terpene |FRAME: SECOLOGANIN-CPD|, which are combined to form |FRAME: STRICTOSIDINE| by |FRAME: EC-4.3.3.2|.
