/
/Like other fatty acids, |FRAME: CPD-12189| is hardly found as a free acid, and is usually found as either |FRAME: 11Z-icos-11-enoyl-ACPs "(11Z)-icos-11-enoyl-[acp]"|, |FRAME: CPD-15363|, or incorporated into lipids.
