TYPES - All-Coas
COMMON-NAME - a (3Z)-alk-3-enoyl-CoA
SYNONYMS - cis-&Delta;<SUP>3</SUP>-enoyl-CoA
SYNONYMS - a <i>cis</i>-&Delta;<SUP>3</SUP>-enoyl-CoA
SYNONYMS - a <i>cis</i>-3-enoyl-CoA
