/A <i>pigG</i> null mutant was generated and found to have a white phenotype, indicating no production of pigment |CITS: [15853884]|. The mutant was shown to produce |FRAME: CPD-17007| (MAP), confirming that it is involved in the biosynthesis of |FRAME: CPD-17013| (MBC).
