/
/In heptamethylated phthioceranic acids, R1,R2,R3 = H.
/In octamethylated phthioceranic acids, R1,R3 = H, R2=CH3.
/In heptamethylated hydroxyphthioceranic acids, R2,R3 = H, R1=OH.
