COMMENT - This compound represents a membrane attached, nascent peptidoglycan polymer with a tetrapeptide stem (<i>meso</i>-diaminopimelate containing). The R group represents a glycan chain of &beta;1,4-linked N-acetylglucosamine and N-acetylmuramic acid residues with peptide stems of varying length (penta-, tetra- and tripeptide) - some of which may be involved in cross-links with other glycan strands.
