UNIQUE-ID - B-antigen
TYPES - blood-group-substances
COMMON-NAME - a B antigen
SYNONYMS - &alpha;-D-galactosyl-(1,3)-(&alpha;-L-fucosyl-(1,2))-&beta;-D-galactosyl-(1,4)-<i>N</i>-acetyl-&beta;-D-glucosamine-(1,3)-&beta;-D-galactosyl-[protein]
